About Me

Hey! I'm Zainab — a frontend developer and digital dream chaser. I'm currently balancing O-Levels while working on real projects that let me bring web interfaces to life. I specialize in crafting responsive, animated websites with a feminine aesthetic. Whether it's React, Next.js, or CSS magic — I'm always exploring and building.
